{
    "comment_thread": {}, 
    "video_length": "PT7M12S", 
    "captions": [
        {
            "text": "Hello.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Let me introduce ourselves:", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "This is Tito", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and I am Tito&#39;s father.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "12 years ago, when he was born,", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I had a name, too.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "But now it&#39;s gone.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I have simply, fully become Tito&#39;s dad", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and in some environments,\nthe soccer environmet in particular,", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Nico&#39;s dad as well.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "You see, I am Manzoni&#39;s Unnamed.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Tito was born with cerebral palsy,", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "which makes it hard for him to move.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "He walks with a walker,", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "that one right there,", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and when the walker\nis not close enough to him,", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "he uses me as his crutch.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I am always ready", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "to help my son, as his crutch.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Because I use him as my crutch,", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and hang on to him.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "He hangs on to me to walk", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and I hang on to him to speak,", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "to think,", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and mostly,", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "since he was born,", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "he helps me to feel.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I have been emotionally paralysed\nfor my entire life,", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and I have to say\nhe is a very powerful crutch.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "TED offers a million dollar prize", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "to those who are able to change the world.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So I should give Tito a milion dollars", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "not because he has changed the world,", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and he never will,", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "but because he changed my world,", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "my tiny miserable world.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "He revolutionized it,\nturned it upside down,", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "curiously enough, always for the best.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "He has become...\nYou are my clean energy,", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "you are everything,", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "you are my universal peace, Tito.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I should give a million dollars\nto my wife, as well", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "because she had the one and only\ngood idea in our lives", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "which you can see in this video.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "In fourth grade, Tito began", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "to walk to school by himself", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "using the ramps\nfrom the Venice Marathon,", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "two ramps, in this case\nfrom the Venice Marathon,", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Anna, my wife, had the great idea", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "of asking - unfortunately to me -\nto film Tito.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "You see I&#39;m not a good cameraman.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "She asked me to film Tito\nwhile he was walking to school,", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and sent it to the Office for the\nElimination of Architectural Barriers", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "of the city of Venice.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Unlike anything you would expect\nfrom a Public Administration,", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "they quickly got around to helping us,", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "efficiently, with no bureaucracy,", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and they kept the ramps\nuntil the end of the school year.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Now the thing has grown", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "because we involved\nthe Guggenheim Museum,", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "which is fully accessible inside", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "but impossible to get to.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "These are some of the problems\nof living in a city.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Laws force the Guggenheim\nto provide all the lifts, etc.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "but you can&#39;t get there.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "But now you can. Thanks to Tito...", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Tito: And thanks to Pinot.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "DM: To Pinot, I&#39;m sorry, also thanks\nto the Fondazione Pinot. Bravo Tito.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "The Fondazione is part of this project.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "(Applause)", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "My crutch is also helpful\nfor my lack of memory.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So, a million dollars to my wife, also", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "because it is very onerous\nto be one&#39;s own TED.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "If you don&#39;t have good ideas yourself", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "you must begin to look around.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And the only thing I can say\nabout our experience,", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "which touched me deep inside,", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and I did write about it,", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "because I experienced it personally\nand quite intensely,", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "is the opposite of that beautiful video", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "we watched,\nthe one about the English girl", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "swimming underwater.\nShe overcame her limitations.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Hers is a story about moving beyond.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "She overcame her barriers.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "As for us. No. We did not.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "We overcame the need to overcome.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "We are past the idea of overcoming,", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "because we live happily,\nwithin our limitations,", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "with our obstacles.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Me, him, his mother, his brother.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "We live well within our limited world,", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "filled with barriers.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "the only barriers we were able to overcome", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "were those two blessed bridges", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "on Tito&#39;s way to school.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "The episode, the key element\nthat truly helped us understand", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "how to overcome the need to overcome,", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "to go beyond the limits,\nto take down the barriers,", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "happened when Tito was 7 months old.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "We had just found out the he,", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "due to a mistake\nof the Venice Hospital -", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I praised the Public Administration,\nbut now I take everything back -", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "because Tito is the consequence\nof a red-handed mistake of the hospital...", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Anyway, when he was 7 months old,", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "right after we received the news,", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I was on the couch reading the paper,\nhe was here, on my lap,", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "his mom was cooking,", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and she tripped on the rug... and boom!\nShe fell on the floor.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Suddenly, Tito burst into a huge laugh,\nand kept laughing hard ...", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "a kind of laugh coming from ...", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "because he is, yes, he loves to laugh", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "in all of these circumstances.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And that was when we realized", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "what was the essence of our lives.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "He falls, but she falls.\nI fall, his brother falls.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "We are a family of falling\nand fallen people.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Thank you.\n(Applause)", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }
    ], 
